<h2>Red (strawberry) tongue, Sore tongue, Swollen tongue and White patches on tongue</h2>
<p>WebMD Symptom Checker helps you find the most common medical conditions indicated by the symptoms red (strawberry) tongue, sore tongue, swollen tongue and white patches on tongue including Scarlet fever, Thermal burn of mouth or tongue, and Drug allergy.</p>
<p>There  are 11 conditions  associated with red (strawberry) tongue, sore tongue, swollen tongue and white patches on tongue. The links below will provide you with more detailed information on these medical conditions from the WebMD Symptom Checker and help provide a better understanding of causes and treatment of these related conditions.</p>
</div>
